5 Sec. 5. LEGISLATIVE INTENT; PRIVATIZATION CONTRACTS
6 It is the intent of the General Assembly that a privatization contract shall
7 not be required for a contract for services when there is no permanent,
8 classified State employee position to perform the equivalent of such proposed
9 contracted services, which includes health services and capital construction.
10 Sec. 6. EFFECTIVE DATES
11 This act shall take effect on passage, except that Sec. 1 shall take effect on
12 July 1, 2026.
